  "description": "A legato lead sitting on the edge of self-resonance. Filter reso at 0.55 — stable, but aware of the precipice. Mod wheel shifts formantIntensity and filterReso simultaneously: at full throw, the cutoff climbs and reso tips into feedback whistling, the crystal lattice achieving coherence. Aftertouch alone drives cascadeBlend — press into a held note and the harmonic cascade multiplies, each overtone unlocking the next. Velocity sets the initial tiltY angle: soft keys come from the side, hard keys strike the center, producing a fundamentally different spectral signature. Performed correctly this preset sounds like a living crystal membrane.",
